WEBVTT

00:00:13.657 --> 00:00:15.745
How big was that fish you caught?

00:00:15.745 --> 00:00:16.832
This big?

00:00:17.107 --> 00:00:17.977
This big?

00:00:18.485 --> 00:00:20.123
This big?

00:00:20.123 --> 00:00:21.499
Without photographic evidence,

00:00:21.499 --> 00:00:23.830
there's nothing that proves you caught a whopper,

00:00:23.830 --> 00:00:26.551
and that's been true since the dawn of fishing.

00:00:26.551 --> 00:00:28.782
In fact, hundreds of years ago,

00:00:28.782 --> 00:00:31.279
long before photography could capture the moment,